      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Relax, Rejuvenate, Beautify</h1>
      <p class="text-lg leading-loose text-gray-600">Treat yourself to a luxurious experience at One Love Beauty Salon. We offer a wide range of hair, nail, and skincare services performed by experienced and passionate professionals. Discover the difference a relaxing and welcoming environment can make. Book your appointment today and step into a world of beauty and wellness.</p>
